00:15:09.840 --> 00:15:10.600
next few slides.

253
00:15:11.960 --> 00:15:15.580
And to show that this compound was actually hitting the target of

254
00:15:15.620 --> 00:15:19.490
interest in cells, we took advantage of cellular thermal shift assays and

255
00:15:19.520 --> 00:15:23.100
