261
00:15:43.020 --> 00:15:46.640
Now, in order to characterize the functional effects of these inhibitors, this work

262
00:15:46.680 --> 00:15:50.170
was led by Jie Luo in the group. And he showed

263
00:15:50.600 --> 00:15:54.460
essentially that these are very potent nanomolar or

264
00:15:54.560 --> 00:15:58.380
picomolar level compounds, and you can see effects in

265
00:15:58.420 --> 00:16:02.040
terms of AR-positive prostate cancer cells shown here in red are

266
00:16:02.080 --> 00:16:05.900
basically the DELTACs at a nanomolar or even picomolar

267
00:16:05.940 --> 00:16:07.760
level, quite potent.

268
00:16:08.780 --> 00:16:12.620
And this is probably starkly shown here with 22RV1 cells, which is again an

