272
00:16:22.240 --> 00:16:26.060
assay. While this is not the case with just using the p300

273
00:16:26.100 --> 00:16:29.860
inhibitor and the AR inhibitor. So we're certainly getting

274
00:16:29.920 --> 00:16:33.390
